Title: Onitinere
DateModified: '2018-02-08'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/onitinere
SetInCountry: Italy
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Vittorio Greco Miani
AuthorCountry: Italy
Text: "Journal of the people met on the road:\nA journal that everyone can share,\
  \ featuring experiences and stories of the \npeople met on the road\n\u25AA Communicative\
  \ code: photographs, videos and stories.\n\u25AA Aim: showing customs and traditions\
  \ of the next \u201COnitinere\u201D journey by \ncollecting stories directly from\
  \ the local people, and by means of breath-taking \nphotographs and travel experiences.\
  \ \n\u25AA Onitinere used both as a collection of stories and producer of contents.\n\
  Discover the world by peeking at people\u2019s lives, \nlistening to experiences,\
  \ and sharing far away \npeople\u2019 stories:\nChannels: which ones should be preferred\
  \ and \nhow to use them\nFacebook: sharing photos and \nexperiences (more informal)\n\
  Instagram: breath-taking pictures\nWhatsapp / Fb Messenger: \ninvitation to further\
  \ discovery by \nlinking to the blog (chatbot)\nYoutube: Vlog format\nONITINERE\
  \ comes from the love of \ntravelling and the craving for new \nexperiences."
